      • toOperator

        public static Operator toOperator(java.lang.Object object)
        Try to convert the given object to an Operator. Primitives according to OperatorUtil.isPrimitive(Class) are returned as OperatorConstantNode. Lists are returned as OperatorListNode Other objects are being dealt with as OperatorStructNode, where only those fields are considered that are annotated with ParameterConfigDoc.
